# Species and Heritage

Before you were a fighter or a wizard, before you chose your calling or picked up your first weapon, you were born into a heritage that shapes how you experience the world. Species represents your innate capabilities—the advantages and perspectives that come from your fundamental nature.

Every species in Autumn Phoenix RPG provides the same mechanical structure: an attribute bonus and three unique traits. These choices matter throughout your career, not just at creation. Your species shapes how you generate Momentum, how you interact with the world, and what unique capabilities you bring to your party.

